# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Foot Holics — website environment variables (Vercel serverless functions)
#
# The site's /api endpoints now use ESPN's KEYLESS public API (scores, fixtures,
# stats, H2H, lineups, standings) — so NO API keys / env vars are required to run
# the website locally or in production.
#
#   Local dev:  vercel dev      (serves the static site + /api endpoints)
#
# (The Telegram bot keeps its own separate config at foot-holics-bot/.env.example.)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# No website env vars are currently required.
